I '''Norman Solomon''' (mibait 1951) metung yang [[Estados Unidos|Americanu]]ng [[peryodista]], [[media studies|kritiko ning media]], [[Peace activist|aktibista kontra gera]], ampong kasalukuyan a kandidatu para king [[United States House of Representatives]]. Malambat neng kaugne ning grupung magbante king mediang [[Fairness & Accuracy In Reporting]] (FAIR).  Anyang 1997, tetag ne ing [[Institute for Public Accuracy]], a manigobra bang mamyeng alternatibung pikukwanan balita para kareng peryodista, at migsilbi yang direktor a talapagpaganap anggang 2010. Makabili ya king pambansang syndication ing kolum nang lulwal balang duminggu, ing "Media Beat", manibat 1992-2009. Mas bayu kaniti, makabili ing pansin nang Solomon king kayang kampanya king banwang  2012 para king Kongreso o Kapulungan ding Pekakatawan, para king kanam a distritung pangkapulungan ning California (California's 6th congressional district).

